OL,3,CJustice minister apologises after
OL,4,Ckiller went on run three times
OL,6,FThe Justice Minister has apologised to
OL,7,Fthe family of a man murdered in
OL,8,FLondonderry in 2007 after his killer
OL,9,Fwent on the run three times.
OL,11,FJames Meehan is now back behind bars
OL,12,Fhaving been arrested in Republic of
OL,13,FIreland last week, with Naomi Long
OL,14,Fhaving now committed to a review of
OL,15,Fthe case.
OL,17,FThe minister said: "I apologise to
OL,18,Fthem for the distress they have been
OL,19,Fthrough and I empathise with the
OL,20,Fchallenge they have faced.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/5
