OL,3,CJustice minister apologises after
OL,4,Ckiller went on run three times
OL,6,F"I've met with other families who've
OL,7,Fbeen in similar situations and I am
OL,8,Fabsolutely convicted of the need to
OL,9,Flook at our system, not to dispense
OL,10,Fwith the pre-release testing because
OL,11,Fthat is essential for public safety
OL,12,Freasons, but to look at how we can
OL,13,Fmake sure we minimise any opportunity
OL,14,Ffor these repeat offenders, when they
OL,15,Fare being tested for release into the
OL,16,Fcommunity, from being able to continue
OL,17,Fthis kind of hamster wheel approach."
OL,19,FMeehan was handed a life sentence back
OL,20,Fin 2009 for the murder of Londonderry
OL,21,Fman Jim McFadden.
