OL,3,CJustice minister apologises after
OL,4,Ckiller went on run three times
OL,6,FThe 42-year-old was repeatedly punched
OL,7,Fin the chest and died from a ruptured
OL,8,Fheart in an attack that took place
OL,9,Foutside his home in Derry after
OL,10,Freturning from his his sister-in-law's
OL,11,Fwedding reception in Donegal in 2007.
OL,13,FThe first time Meehan went on the run
OL,14,Fwas during his trial for murder in
OL,15,F2009.
OL,17,FThe second occasion was back in 2022.
OL,18,FMeehan had been allowed to live in
OL,19,FLimavady, but it was discovered he
OL,20,Fwasn't living there, and a warrant was
OL,21,Fissued for his arrest.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/5
