OL,3,CJustice minister apologises after
OL,4,Ckiller went on run three times
OL,6,FHe spent over a year hiding from the
OL,7,Fauthorities.
OL,9,FJames Meehan is now back in prison
OL,10,Fafter spending nearly nine months
OL,11,Froaming free for a third time.
OL,13,FHe was on day release from Magilligan
OL,14,FPrison last December - Meehan finally
OL,15,Fcaptured last week in the Republic.
OL,17,FHe was brought before the High Court
OL,18,Fand remanded in custody to appear
OL,19,Fagain on the 10th of September.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/5
