OL,3,CJustice minister apologises after
OL,4,Ckiller went on run three times
OL,6,F"If somebody is not serious about
OL,7,Fgrasping the opportunities that we
OL,8,Foffer them for rehabilitation and
OL,9,Freform, then we have to look at some
OL,10,Fway of giving the families at least
OL,11,Fsome respite from that relentless
OL,12,Fchange and that relentless process for
OL,13,Ftheir own mental health and
OL,14,Fwellbeing," said Naomi Long.
OL,16,F"We have to keep victims at the center
OL,17,Fof all that we do."
